No. 11-5641. Jose Gonzalez, Petitioner v. Florida. 565 U.S. 936, 132 S. Ct. 387,

181 L. Ed. 2d 243,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 6251. October 3, 2011.

Motion of Florida Association of Criminal Defense Lawyers for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the District Court of Appeal of Florida, First District, denied.

Same case below, 50 So. 3d 633.
